HEADWORD: By-view
<hw>By"-view`</hw><pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A private or
selfish view; self-interested aim or purpose.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>No <qex>by-views</qex> of his own shall mislead him.</q>
<rj><qau>Atterbury.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

